Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). Within cs.CL, the paper is likely to fall under sub-categories related to parsing, such as cs.CL (Computation and Language) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper proposes a new algorithm for parsing, which could also place it in categories related to machine learning and algorithms, such as cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
